narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I recommend this class 100%. Everyone works very hard, so as long as you're willing to put in an hour to two hours a night of practice, you will love it.
